{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here we are.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're finally free, but we're quarantined.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've got a fence around us again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but, you know, they knew what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they disinfected us and everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after like 10 or 12 days, they let us out to the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by that time, the Russians were in the-- were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we saw piles, lines and lines of soldiers-- German soldiers walking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It just-- I can end it up-- we-- I got terribly sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got terribly sick with typhus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Terrible-- the people died of typhus, like nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Terrible temperatures.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took me-- somebody took me, whatever, to their-- to a makeshift Russian hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember getting any medicine, or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember getting some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I think I was unconscious for days, and days, and days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was like, you know, on the borderline of-- I think I was dying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was just a matter of one way or the other, going over that edge, because I know I was unconscious with very high fever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But somehow or other, I-- I survived that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was taken from there into a-- into a house where all the young people were housed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was, like, convalescing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I heard my name, Sevek, which is my Polish name, being called.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I look out the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And below me was my brother, in Theresienstadt, carrying a knapsack, German knapsack on his shoulder.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he had food, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so, naturally, this is how we got reunited.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was a very happy moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have-- I had a lot of feelings about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very happy moment to have my brother back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- that was really terrific.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
